{"tid":1592541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【學術討論】十一試下connect中國維權人士？","createTime":"2019-09-24T16:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T17:48:22.000Z","uid":175123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d25b68bb0bf66f5c22046c324dc27e1e92e166d1","tid":1592541,"uid":175123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:06:36.000Z","msg":"黃金週不嬲都好多同胞嚟玩，一定要大大力歡迎佢地，比佢地感受下香港嘅節日氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae0f6f66f145f873a9956a7b563d9b0f1d74f80","tid":1592541,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"d2e52b7683077b53e8f9faf477e48bf17587b028","tid":1592541,"uid":175123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:15:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c60abec28ae9f48bb9772cd897a71b60e90a247","tid":1592541,"uid":175123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:29:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fedbe7dd015e6a532468a6ce2fd7f4caa287656c","tid":1592541,"uid":289846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:30:35.000Z","msg":"老兵「十一」集結 籲全民上街推翻中共<br />\n<br />\n【新唐人北京時間2019年09月24日訊】持續3個多月的香港反送中運動已經蔓延至中國大陸。近日，多方消息披露，退伍老兵將在「十一」維權，聯合現役軍人齊聚北京，並呼籲所有維權群體能夠一起上街，推翻中共政權！<br />\n<br />\n據報，中國現有退役軍人5700多萬，並以每年幾十萬的速度遞增。多年以來，大量退伍老兵維權，他們主要的訴求是解決生活待遇等問題。然而這些曾經為中共賣命的軍人與中國其他維權群體一樣，合理訴求得不到解決，反而成了中共的維穩對像，遭到殘酷打壓。<br />\n<br />\n眼見中共70週年「十一」慶典將至，受香港反送中運動鼓舞，多方消息披露，退伍老兵將在「十一」維權。<br />\n<br />\n一名自稱退伍老兵錄製視頻呼籲，藉此次全國各地要舉辦中共建政70週年活動之際，希望所有維權人士都去參加，一邊參加慶祝活動一邊進行維權，並提出各自的訴求，人多力量大，全國大連動。<br />\n<br />\n該退伍老兵同時請求大家向各地維權群體廣泛傳播這消息。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，「為了維護『十一』期間的社會穩定，黨中央和國務院已經向各級黨委、政法委、中央機關下達命令，要他們做好預防性措施，避免出現群體事件，黨強調絕不能破壞節日氣氛。<br />\n..................<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/09/24/a102671476.html?fbclid=IwAR1f9D16Tty3O4-T1trJzeZMlIYHbZuDJKN272iAxMX53QHAFwKSUVocCQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F09%2F24%2Fa102671476.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1f9D16Tty3O4-T1trJzeZMlIYHbZuDJKN272iAxMX53QHAFwKSUVocCQw&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=5379ac7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/09/24/a102671476.html?fbclid=IwAR1f9D16Tty3O4-T1trJzeZMlIYHbZuDJKN272iAxMX53QHAFwKSUVocCQw</a>"},{"pid":"1bbc3cf91f1c43d596d332af1b813936afbf2394","tid":1592541,"uid":175123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:37:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91b66cb4ab42d238baa789d136783e176901ff00","tid":1592541,"uid":175123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:48:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1f7662d3706f174728b3e058931e3ccbf2d5e87","tid":1592541,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:48:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">929 同101 要聲援新疆！</span></span><br />\n將香港抗爭視野帶去有<ins>國際使命感既層次</ins><br />\n將香港抗爭成為世人既共同任務!!<br />\n有提議<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黑布蒙眼靜坐行動(舉標語) </span></strong></span>, 以令世界關注新疆人權問題。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IsDCpBPjDv0/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FIsDCpBPjDv0%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=79f1a2bc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}